label lbl_store_takeover:
    scene bg comicbookstore_day
    #[Comic Book Store, Afternoon - “Store takeover”  - hitomi_path = 7]

    #[Scene plays out automatically upon entering the comic book shop a day after
    # the previous scene if the player passed the initial Strength 5 requirement.
    # If they didn’t, it will play automatically once they reach the requirement
    # and enter the shop]

    #[If the player hasn’t reached the strength requirement, then when they click
    # the shop they’ll receive a message reminding them they need a minimum of
    # Strength 5 to proceed with the storyline]

    #-Scene begins with Mc entering the shop only to witness Lord Kev, Crugeon
    # and Davendithas talking amongst themselves and clearly annoyed about getting
    # kicked out of their nerd cave-
    show pov embarrassed at left
    show lor angry_talk at Position(xpos=900)
    show cru shocked at Position(xpos=1200)
    show dav neutral at Position(xpos=1500)
    with dissolve
    lor "This is an outrage! A travesty! A downright insult to the rule of the crown of Azanthor that would have resulted in downright demands for execution in the Kingdoms of Renakh’aer!"
    show lor confused at Position(xpos=900)
    show cru embarrassed_talk at Position(xpos=1200)
    cru "Um, actually. After the revolts that lead to the revolution of the princess of the winds from the east and the subsequent coronation of Galileus Girthlenght and his council of Merry Men-"
    show pov confused at left
    show cru bored_talk at Position(xpos=1200)
    cru "Executions and any and all acts of public punishment and violent displays of the like, were banned after he authorized the inclusion of his addendum of new air traffic laws for dragon riders."
    show cru angry_talk at Position(xpos=1200)
    cru "But I do share the sentiment you were meaning to say!"
    cru "How can Hitomi just kick us out of our space like this?!"

    show cru bored at Position(xpos=1200)
    show dav neutral at Position(xpos=1500)
    dav "*Silent but Agreeing Nod showing Displeasure*"
    show pov bored at left
    show lor angry_talk at Position(xpos=900)
    show dav neutral at Position(xpos=1500)


    dav "{i}*Silent but agreeing nod showing displeasure*{/i}"

    lor "This is an utter betrayal! We have been banished from our domains and forced to mingle amongst those of the mortal realms!"
    lor "This is worse than the release of the extra special edition of Galactic Conflicts or when they tried to adapt the saga of Ghost Waifu Mega Milkies into a live action adaptation and replaced the main heroine with a woman who barely had a B-cup!"
    show lor shocked at Position(xpos=900)
    show cru angry_talk at Position(xpos=1200)
    cru "This might be even worse than the ending of Game of-"
    show pov shocked at left
    show lor angry_talk at Position(xpos=900)
    show cru angry at Position(xpos=1200)
    lor "Woah, easy there, Crugeon. You know well that nothing can ever be that terrible. And we all agree to never speak of it again so we could enjoy the prequel series while entirely ignoring the events of the main one."

    show lor angry at Position(xpos=900)
    show dav neutral at Position(xpos=1500)
    dav "*Slow Nod of Mutual Understanding*"
    show pov confused at left
    show cru confused_talk at Position(xpos=1200)


    dav "{i}*Slow nod of mutual understanding*{/i}"

    cru "You are right, you are right…"
    show lor confused at Position(xpos=900)
    show cru bored_talk at Position(xpos=1200)
    cru "I’m just so upset about this that I seem to be letting my emotions get the best of me!"
    show cru smirk_talk at Position(xpos=1200)
    cru "Truly not something worthy of a level 75 Vulcanic Psychic Wizard… My atoms would have been pulverized for such a display of emotion, had we been in game!"
    show pov smirk at left
    show lor smirk_talk at Position(xpos=900)
    show cru bored at Position(xpos=1200)
    lor "As long as you are aware of it, we can let such things slide due to the circumstances."
    show pov shocked at left
    show lor bored_talk at Position(xpos=900)
    lor "Regardless though, this is truly an outrage of fantastical proportions!"
    show pov confused_talk at left
    show lor shocked at Position(xpos=900)
    pov "Something wrong with the fellowship, you guys?"
    show pov shocked at left
    show lor angry_talk at Position(xpos=900)
    lor "YOU!"
    show pov shocked_talk at left
    show lor angry at Position(xpos=900)
    show cru smirk at Position(xpos=1200)
    pov "Me?"
    show pov confused at left
    show lor angry_talk at Position(xpos=900)
    lor "You Betrayer! Kingslayer! Colonizer of Kingdoms!"
    show pov smirk_talk at left
    show lor angry at Position(xpos=900)
    show cru confused at Position(xpos=1200)
    pov "Woah, woah, woah. What’s going on with you guys?"
    show pov smirk at left
    show lor smirk at Position(xpos=900)
    show cru angry_talk at Position(xpos=1200)
    show dav bored at Position(xpos=1500)
    cru "You should know quite well what’s going on. You have taken our lands!"
    show pov smirk_talk at left
    show cru angry at Position(xpos=1200)
    pov "Oh… Is this about the nerd cave?"
    show pov neutral_talk at left
    pov "Yeah, I’m sorry guys, I promised to help Hitomi out with her art practice and we needed some space for her to work in."
    show pov neutral at left
    show lor smirk_talk at Position(xpos=900)
    lor "But why must we be banished into the realm of mortals from our sanctuary for her to do so?!"
    show pov confused_talk at left
    show lor confused at Position(xpos=900)
    pov "Can you guys promise not to criticize her work or make references to other nerdy stuff and anatomy examples that make her feel uncomfortable?"
    show pov confused at left
    show lor smirk_talk at Position(xpos=900)
    show cru smirk at Position(xpos=1200)
    lor "…"
    lor "Well played, young knight…"
    show pov bored_talk at left
    show lor smirk at Position(xpos=900)
    show hit shocked at Position(xpos=1800)
    pov "Yeah, I thought as much."
    show pov neutral_talk at left
    pov "Look guys, it’s just for a while. And considering Hitomi lets you guys hoard the place for yourselves most of the time, I’m sure you guys can do her a solid, just this once."
    pov "Besides, her family owns the place to begin with, so she gets to decide what to do with that space regardless, you know?"
    show pov embarrassed at left
    show lor confused at Position(xpos=900)
    show cru bored_talk at Position(xpos=1200)
    cru "That’s… a good point with sound logic…"
    show cru bored at Position(xpos=1200)
    show dav neutral at Position(xpos=1500)
    dav "*Slow Nod of Shame*"
    show pov neutral_talk at left
    show cru bored at Position(xpos=1200)


    dav "{i}*Slow nod of shame*{/i}"
    pov "You guys can survive without your cave for a day. Why not go to the beach and maybe get some color on your skin or mess around in the water?"
    show pov bored at left
    show cru shocked_talk at Position(xpos=1200)
    cru "Kevlamin gets sunburnt really easily and we have an agreement between the three of us to never put on each other’s sunscreen."
    show lor bored_talk at Position(xpos=900)
    lor "Silence, or I will have you beheaded by my level 89 Hydra Rider Dominatrix!"
    show lor smirk_talk at Position(xpos=900)
    lor "Nevertheless, I see your point. And as a benevolent ruler, I shall allow our retainer to use our holy domain in the further pursuit of her creative horizons!"
    lor "But just for today because we forgot to pay for use of the room in advance this month!"
    show lor confused at Position(xpos=900)
    show hit embarrassed_talk at Position(xpos=1800)
    with dissolve
    hit "[povname]?"
    hit "Are you out there?"
    show pov neutral_talk at left
    show lor confused at Position(xpos=900)
    show cru confused at Position(xpos=1200)
    show dav bored at Position(xpos=1500)
    show hit confused at Position(xpos=1800)
    pov "I’m coming, Hitomi!"
    show pov embarrassed_talk at left
    pov "Thanks for being understanding, you guys. I’m sure Hitomi really appreciates you are allowing her to use her own space."
    show pov neutral_talk at left
    pov "I’ll see you all later."
    show pov embarrassed at left
    show lor smirk_talk at Position(xpos=900)
    show cru smirk at Position(xpos=1200)
    show hit bored at Position(xpos=1800)
    lor "Faretheewells!"
    show lor smirk at Position(xpos=900)
    show cru neutral at Position(xpos=1200)
    cru "Live Long and Bone Faster."
    show dav neutral at Position(xpos=1500)
    dav "*Silent Nod of Goodbye’s*"


    #-Scene fades to black to indicate transition as MC moves from the front to the back and the guys leave-

    #=SCENE END=

    scene black
    with fade

    jump lbl_strike_a_pose
